In a small bowl, stir cream cheese until smooth. Gradually stir in mustard until smooth and well blended, stir in pepper. Spread 1 tablespoon mixture on each of 4 slices of bread. Top each with a lettuce leaf, 2 tomato slices and 3 slices of ham. Spread 1-1/2 Tbsp. prepared guacamole onto each of the remaining 4 slices of bread; sprinkle with red pepper flakes, if desired, place guacamole side down on the ham. Serve immediately.